title: on me by section 1 (2) of the Credit Union (Amendment) Act 2023 (No. 34 of
heading: 2. The 30th day of September 2024 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 30th day of September 2024 is appointed as the day on which the 
following provisions of the Credit Union (Amendment) Act 2023 (No. 34 of 
2023) shall come into operation: 

(a) 

paragraphs (a) and (b) of section 18; 

(b) 

section 26; 

(c) 

section 29. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

18 September, 2024. 

JACK CHAMBERS, 

Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 24th September, 2024.
